<p>Our goal at eLife is to publish papers that our editors and reviewers find authoritative, rigorous, insightful, enlightening &ldquo;or just beautiful&rdquo;. The 1,000 research papers we&rsquo;ve published to date range from the most fundamental and theoretical work, through to translational, applied, and clinical research.</p>
	<p>Get a flavour for eLife with your free copy of our limited edition print highlights.</p>
